Install the Fix
Run &quot;Install_32bit.bat&quot; from the main folder
Change name in SmartSteamEmu.ini by &quot;PersonaName&quot;
Play the game with SmartSteamLoader.exe

Installation for x64:
Install the Fix
Run &quot;Install_64bit.bat&quot; from the main folder
Change name in 3DMGAME.ini by &quot;UserName&quot;
